### Get transactions with pagination, filters and sorting

GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?{{PLN}}&{{category}}&{{date}}&{{amount}}&{{sorting}}&{{pagination}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get sum of amounts of filtered transactions

GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/analysis?{{PLN}}&{{date2}}&{{type}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### GET STATISTICS ABOUT TRANSACTIONS
@omitCategory = omitCategory=myAccount&omitCategory=investments
@yearAndMonth = year=2023

GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/statistics?{{type}}&{{PLN}}&{{yearAndMonth}}&{{omitCategory}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get all transactions (still default pagination is applied)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get single transaction
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}
Accept: application/json

### Create new transaction

# @name createTransaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "date": "2015-09-24",
  "description": "ASEC W-wa Ratusz Ar/Warszawa",
  "amount": 1.70,
  "currency": "PLN",
  "category": "transport",
  "transactionType": "expense",
  "paymentMethod": "card",
  "account": "mBank",
  "currencies": "PLN/CZK",
  "exchangeRate": 1.5
}

### Update a transaction (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{wzTransactionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{ 
  "date": "2015-9-24",
  "description": "ASEC W-wa Ratusz Ar/Warszawa some change",
  "amount": 1.70,
  "currency": "PLN",
  "category": "transport",
  "transactionType": "expense",
  "paymentMethod": "card",
  "account": "mBank"
}

### Partial update of transaction (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{wzTransactionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "description": "tratata",
  "amount": 7.77
}

